---
title: Chicken Breast Souvlaki Dinner Plate with Dilly Rice and Feta Sauce
description: Chicken that has been kissed by bright lemony flavour teams perfectly with buttery dill rice and fresh salad. Tangy feta-dill sauce is dolloped on top to round this meal out!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/souvlaki-de-poitrines-de-poulet-6e0db09c.jpg
